================================================================================
                      TROUBLESHOOTING
================================================================================

If the service fails to start:
1. Check systemd status:
   sudo systemctl status {{ vepc_service_name }}

2. View detailed logs:
   sudo journalctl -u {{ vepc_service_name }} -n 200 --no-pager

3. Verify configuration files:
   ls -la {{ config_path }}/

4. Check network connectivity:
   ip addr show

5. Verify port binding:
   netstat -tlnup | grep -E '{{ gtp_c_port }}|{{ s1ap_port }}|{{ diameter_port }}|{{ cli_port }}'

